LANGSIDE Hall Trust is seeking the opinions of local people to help develop a future for the building. Have your say on Langside Hall LANGSIDE Hall Trust is seeking the opinions of local people to help develop a future for the building.The Trust was formed in 2013 to deal with the transfer of the hall from Glasgow City Council to the community.Community Enterprise is helping the Trust with research to establish what the needs are in the local area.To help, you can fill in the form at www.surveymonkey.com/s/Langside _ Hall_Trust 